text: Yalkae, a Joker in High School () is a 1977 South Korean family comedy movie directed by Seok Rae-myeong and starring Jeong Yun-hui, Hah Myung-joong, Lee Seung-hyeon, Kim Jeong-hun. ==Other websites== * Category:1977 comedy movies Category:1970s family movies Category:South Korean movies Category:Movies directed by Seok Rae-Myeong
title: Yalkae, a Joker in High School
